snippet.title: TWHL Tower: Source Release Trailer
snippet.description:
TWHL Tower: Source is out now! Get it on ModDB.
https://www.moddb.com/mods/twhl-tower-source

TWHL Tower: Source is a collaborative Half-Life 2 mod where you climb a tower where each floor is made by a different creator.

Trailer by cambreaKer. Sector Sweep mix by Aqualuzara.
